title: David Bowie Acoustic Performances 1997
description:
I don&#039;t know if this is one performance or a collection of them. I do know that most (if not all) of the tracks were recorded in 1997 or shortly after, and all tracks are acoustic performances. If anyone knows the source of this, please let me know, I&#039;m curious!  

The songs are:

1. Scary Monsters and Super Creeps
2. Seven Years in Tibet
3. The Supermen
4. Dead Man Walking
5. The Jean Genie
6. I Can&#039;t Read
7. Quicksand
8. Aladdin Sane
9. The Man Who Sold the World
10. The Supermen
11. Andy Warhol
12. Repetition
